            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(M) In nomine Dei eterni. Anno eius incarnationis millesimo centesimo
                        tricesimo primo, sexto idus iunii, indicione nona. <rs key="#Churches"
                            >Ecclesie</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Churches #Abbots #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Offersio/donatio #Mansi #Agricultural_workers #Landed_possessions #Petiae #Oil #Slave_labour #Slave"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/2001">Sancti Benedicti</orgName> et vobis domno
                            <persName key="#Abbots #Churches" ref="#people/3568">Heinrico</persName>
                        eiusdem ecclesie <rs key="#Abbots">abbati</rs> et vestre <orgName
                            key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/2420">ecclesie de <placeName
                                key="#Churches" ref="#places/4108">Campo Syon</placeName></orgName>.
                        Ego <persName
                            key="#Lombard #marriage #parentOf #parentInLawOf #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Offersio/donatio #Mansi #Agricultural_workers #Landed_possessions #Petiae #Oil #Slave_labour #Slave"
                            ref="#people/3577">Ionathas</persName>, qui lege <rs key="#Lombard">Longobardorum</rs>
                        vivere videor, una cum <persName
                            key="#marriage #parentOf #parentInLawOf #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Offersio/donatio #Mansi #Agricultural_workers #Landed_possessions #Petiae #Oil #Slave_labour #Slave"
                                ><name ref="Elica">Elica</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#marriage">uxor</rs> mea et <persName
                            key="#childInLawOf #marriage #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Offersio/donatio #Mansi #Agricultural_workers #Landed_possessions #Petiae #Oil #Slave_labour #Slave"
                                ><name ref="Cesaria">Cesaria</name></persName> quondam <rs
                            key="#childInLawOf">nurus</rs> mea, pro remedio anime <persName
                            key="#childOf #marriage"><name ref="Turingus">Turingi</name></persName>,
                            <rs key="#childOf">filii</rs> nostri et prefate nurus nostre viri
                        defuncti, et pro anime nostre et parentum nostrorum mercede, donamus,
                        offerimus et <rs key="#Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure">iure proprietario</rs>
                        habendum statuimus, id est iuris proprietatis nostre quatuor <rs
                            key="#Mansi">mansos</rs> in <placeName key="#Mansi" ref="#places/4430">Tasino</placeName>,
                        unus secundum quod <rs key="#Agricultural_workers">detineri et excoli</rs>
                        visum est per <persName key="#Agricultural_workers"><name ref="Paduinus"
                                >Paduinum</name></persName>, alius per <persName
                            key="#Agricultural_workers"><name ref="Natalis"
                            >Natalem</name></persName>, tercius per <persName
                            key="#Agricultural_workers"><name ref="Martinum/Volta">Martinum
                                Voltam</name></persName>, quartus per <persName
                            key="#Agricultural_workers #Specialized_workers"><name
                                ref="Petrus/piscator">Petrus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Specialized_workers">piscatorem</rs>; et duos mansos in <placeName
                            key="#Mansi" ref="#places/4111">Angarano</placeName>, unus secundum quod
                        detineri et excoli visum est per <persName key="#Agricultural_workers"><name
                                ref="Raginbaldus">Rambaldum</name></persName> da Zurzun, alius per
                            <persName key="#Agricultural_workers"><name ref="Bonusfilius"
                                >Bonumfilium</name></persName>; et <rs key="#Landed_possessions"
                            >sedimen</rs> quod fuit <persName
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Agricultural_workers"><name ref="Waldinus"
                                >Gualdini</name></persName>, et <rs key="#Petiae">peciam</rs> unam
                        de terra cum <rs key="#Oil">olivis</rs> eidem sedimini coherentem, sicuti
                        vobils consignati fecimus, et secundum quod ad suprascriptos mansos
                        pertinere videtur, cum omnibus suis pertinentiis et servitutibus, et omnia
                        in integrum; et <rs key="#Slave_labour #Slave">servum</rs> unum nomine
                            <persName key="#Slave_labour #Slave"><name ref="Iordanus"
                                >Iordanum</name></persName>, seu etiam alio nomine nuncupatum, nulli
                        alii qui supra legitur donata vel tradita nisi vobis suprascripto domno
                        abbati vestreque ecclesie, pro remedio anime iamdicti Turingi defuncti et
                        nostre mercede, ut diximus. Quidem et spondemus atque promittimus nos qui
                        supra Ionathas et Elica et Cesaria, suprascripti Turingi quondam uxor,
                        suprascriptam <rs key="#Offersio/donatio">offersionem et donationem</rs> ut
                        supra legitur ab omni homine defensare et guarentare; quod si defendere vel
                        guarentare omnia que supra leguntur non potuerimus aut si vobis iamdicto
                        domno abbaii et vestre ecclesie aliquid exinde quovis ingenio subtrahere
                        quesierimus, tunc <rs key="#Penalty">in duplum</rs> iamscriptam offersionern
                        restituamus, ita ut pro tempore fuerit meliorata aut valuerit, sub
                        estimatione in consimilibus locis. Actum in Camposyon. Devote. +++ Signa
                        manuum suprascriptorum Ionathe et Elice et Cesarie, qui hanc cartulam fieri
                        rogaverunt. + Signum manus Gualdini, qui hanc cartulam confirmavit et
                        laudavit et testis interfuit. ++++ Signa <rs key="#Witness">testium</rs>:
                            <persName key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio"><name ref="Bertelasus"
                                >Bertelasii</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio"><name ref="Heinricus/de Collo"
                                >Heinrici</name></persName> de Collo, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio"><name ref="Oliverius/de Sivizano"
                                >Oliverii</name></persName> de Sivizano, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio"><name ref="Bertaldus/de Villa"
                                >Bertaldi</name></persName> de Villa. Ego <persName
                            key="#Notary #Writer #Offersio/donatio" ref="#people/3576"
                            >Heinricus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> rogatus <rs key="#Writer">scripsi</rs>. </ab>
                </div>
